WE OFFER FIOS TV AND VERIZONS FIBER-OPTIC VIDEO SERVICE AND

MARKET A VARIETY OF DIRECTV PACKAGES THAT ARE DELIVERED OVER SATELLITE SYSTEMS. FIOS TV PROVIDES ACCESS TO MORE THAN 565 ALL-DIGITAL CHANNELS AND MORE THAN 125 HIGH DEFINITION CHANNELS AND NOW IS AVAILABLE TO APPROXIMATELY 11.7 MILLION HOMES

ACROSS 14 STATES: NEW YORK, NEW JERSEY, CALIFORNIA, DELAWARE, TEXAS, FLORIDA, MARYLAND, PENNSYLVANIA, INDIANA, MASSACHUSETTS, VIRGINIA, RHODE ISLAND, OREGON AND WASHINGTON. INNOVATIVE FEATURES THAT WE BELIEVE DIFFERENTIATE FIOS TV FROM THE

COMPETITION INCLUDE.

