FIOS TV WIDGETS

 VIEWERS GET ONE-TOUCH, ON DEMAND ACCESS TO LOCAL WEATHER, TRAFFIC AND COMMUNITY INFORMATION AND INCREASINGLY POPULAR

SOCIAL MEDIA APPLICATIONS SUCH AS FACEBOOK AND TWITTER. WE ARE EXPANDING WIDGET CAPABILITIES TO SUPPORT ONLINE COMMERCE AND RECENTLY LAUNCHED A HOME SHOPPING NETWORK WIDGET THAT ENABLES PURCHASES VIA REMOTE CONTROL; WE ARE IN DISCUSSION WITH OTHER

COMPANIES TO PURSUE SIMILAR REVENUE-SHARING OPPORTUNITIES. THE WIDGET PLATFORM HAS EVOLVED TO AN OPEN-DEVELOPMENT ENVIRONMENT, INVITING THIRD PARTIES TO CAPTURE OPPORTUNITIES FOR ENHANCED CUSTOMER FEATURES VIA THE FIOS TV PRODUCT. GAMING IS ANOTHER

KEY OPPORTUNITY THAT WILL BE ENABLED THROUGH THE WIDGETS PLATFORM.

